            "id": 6322806,
            "title": "盤中速報 - Atlassian Corporation - Class A(TEAM-US)大漲5.02%，報138.36美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Atlassian Corporation - Class A(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TEAM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TEAM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TEAM-US</a>)截至台北時間27日04:05股價上漲6.61美元，報138.36美元，漲幅5.02%，成交量4,017,859（股），盤中最高價138.36美元、最低價132.51美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.72%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.64%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.61%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-0.21%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>Atlassian Corporation - Class A(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TEAM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TEAM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TEAM-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+11.6%</li> <li>近 1 月：-19.25%</li> <li>近 3 月：-18.99%</li> <li>近 6 月：-35.1%</li> <li>今年以來：-14.87%</li></ul></section></main>",
